Maintainer: The package maintainer is Ayrton Rua <ayrton.gomesmartinsrua@unil.ch>
Description: The package provides an interactive Shiny map allowing the user (traveller) to obtain relevant and useful, easy to access information about cities/monuments of interest, using Twitter and Tripadvisor data. It allows also to query Twitter to obtain information about the popularity of different keywords (e.g. London) over time.
